strings.Value: "A gloomy crowd, angry cries, axes and pitchforks... I can't but recall my younger years in Galt."
"It was our duty to give them a chance to change their minds. But the terrible events of the past days have stoked their minds to a fevered pitch."
"I don't judge... but if they jump at me with weapons, I make my answer quick."
"Like a bustling ant-hill in the face of a wild fire."
"People have different faces, skin and eyes... But the vicious cries of the crowd are the same in every country!"
